{
  "id": "adv_card_kor_01_03",
  "title": "fran 3話 全て嘘？",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（もう、夜中の三時だ……）\n（でも、franさんがまだ残ってるんだよな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（It's already 3 AM…）\n（But fran-san is still here…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.4,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5233.333333299999,
          "startTime": 8.6333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 8.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 8.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です\nコーヒーと、あとそこで夜食を買ってきました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello.\nI brought coffee and some late-night snacks.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 14.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "あら、こんな遅くまで残ってたんですか？\n明日もあなた仕事ですよね、マネージャーさん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ were you working this late too?\nYou have work tomorrow as well‚ right‚ Manager-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "こっちから頼んで、俺だけ寝る訳にはいきませんよ\n……その、デザインの修正はどんな感じです？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can't just ask you for things and then go to sleep myself.\nSo‚ how's the design revision going?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 30.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "まだです\nただ……まぁ、なんとなく方向性は見えてきました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not finished yet.\nBut‚ well‚ I have a general direction in mind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "今まで服のデザインばっかり勉強してたから\nグッズみたいなシンプルなのは少し勝手が違いますけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've mostly studied clothing designs before‚\nso working on simpler items like merchandise is a bit different.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 44.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱ、さっき描いたやつの方が……\nメモどこにやったかしら、えーと確かこの辺に……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ I think the one I drew earlier…\nWhere did I put my notes? It was around here…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "ごてごてしてない方が格好いいんだけど\nでも、シンプルなのが一番難しい。それが真理よね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Minimalistic designs look cooler‚\nbut they're also the most challenging. That's the truth‚ you know…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 62.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、凄いですね\nモデルなのにデザインも経営もやってらしたなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's quite impressive.\nBeing a model and managing designs and business.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "マネージャーなのに、デザインや株にうつつを抜かして\n本業を疎かにするなとは言わないんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though you're a manager‚ you don't say anything about\nabsorbing in designs and stocks‚ and telling me to focus on my primary job?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 76.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "てっきり、体調管理しろとか夜更かし厳禁とか\nくどくど説教されるかと思ってましたけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought you'd lecture me about\ntaking care of my health and not staying up late.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "前の事務所のマネージャーにはよく嫌味言われましたし\n経営のアドバイスもくれませんでしたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My previous manager used to make snide remarks\nand never gave me any business advice either.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 91.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "本当は良くないのかもしれませんが……\n全力で取り組んでるものを、邪魔したくはないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It might not be the best approach‚ but…\nI don't want to interfere with something you're fully committed to.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "みんながそれぞれ輝こうとするのを手伝うのが\nマネージャーの仕事だと思ってますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I believe a manager's job is\nto help each person shine in their own way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 104.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "ふーん……\n事務所が変わると、考え方もいろいろ違うものですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm…\nChanging agencies brings about different perspectives‚ it seems.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 111.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "コーヒーありがとうございました\nじゃ、さっさと出てって一人にして下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for the coffee.\nNow‚ please leave and let me be alone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "後はこれを、朝までに清書しないといけないので！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have to finalize this by morning!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――イベント当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Day of event",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.9
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ステージお疲れ様でした\n次まで少し時間があるので、ゆっくり休んで下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Great job on the stage.\nYou have some time until the next one‚ so take a rest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-kor012.m4a",
      "text": "モデルの時は、何度も着替えて出ずっぱりだったもの\n二回ステージに上がるくらいは全然平気です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I was a model‚ I had to change outfits multiple times and stay busy.\nGoing on stage twice is no problem at all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-kor013.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、ちょっと外に出て来ていいですか？\nなるべく目立たないようにするから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ can I go outside for a moment?\nI'll make sure not to attract too much attention…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "物販ブースさっき見て来ましたけど、大盛況でしたよ\n小さな子達も、ちゃんとバッグに付けてくれてました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I just checked the merchandise booth‚ and it was a huge success.\nEven the little ones were attaching them to their bags properly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-kor014.m4a",
      "text": "本当に！？\nあー、良かったぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really!?\nAh‚ that's a relief…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-kor015.m4a",
      "text": "通学バッグにも付けられるようなデザインにしたし\n気に入って使ってくれるといいんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I designed it to be attachable to school bags as well.\nI hope they like using it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-kor016.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、次のグッズ作る予定はあります？\nあるなら、今度は早めに言って下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ do you have plans for the next merchandise?\nLet me know in advance this time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-kor017.m4a",
      "text": "また直前でリテイクなんてのはごめんなので！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't want last-minute retakes!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ふぁ……はは、すっかりやる気ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha‚ you're really motivated.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 178.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-kor018.m4a",
      "text": "ところで、{user}さんも眠そうですね\n……昨日、徹夜で全部ラッピングしてたからですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ {user}‚ you look sleepy.\nDid you stay up all night wrapping everything?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、まあ……納品が直前になってしまったんで\n俺が自分でやるしかなかったですからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ yeah… The delivery deadline was approaching‚\nso I had no choice but to do it myself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 191.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 194.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-kor019.m4a",
      "text": "あの数のグッズを一人で包装するなんて信じられない\nおたくの事務所、絶対スタッフ足りてないですよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can't believe you wrapped all those items by yourself.\nYour agency definitely needs more staff…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 198.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "まあ、俺はマネージャーの仕事が好きなんですよ\nそれに、この業界も悪いとこじゃないと思いますけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I enjoy being a manager.\nAnd I don't think this industry is all bad either.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 206.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 211.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-kor020.m4a",
      "text": "……知ってます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 211.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-kor021.m4a",
      "text": "いくらお金が稼げるからって、全く楽しくないなら\n移籍してまでアイドル続けたりはしませんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if I can make a lot of money‚ if it's not enjoyable at all‚\nI wouldn't continue being an idol even after switching agencies.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 217.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 220.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-kor022.m4a",
      "text": "ま、ファッションの次くらいにですけどね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ it's next to fashion for me‚ at least!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 220.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――二度目のステージ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "―― Second Stage",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 225.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 227.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-kor023.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロに移籍してから……\nええ、前とはいろいろやり方が違って大変は大変ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since I transferred to Hoshimi Pro…\nYes‚ things have been quite different from before and quite challenging.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 231.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-kor024.m4a",
      "text": "先日、マネージャーさんと意見が分かれて\n私もほんの少し言い返してしまったんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The other day‚ I had a disagreement with my manager‚\nand I spoke back a little.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 241.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-kor025.m4a",
      "text": "でも、後になってみたら\nマネージャーさんの言う方が正しかったんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But looking back‚\nmy manager was right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-kor026.m4a",
      "text": "それに私のことを信じて、いろいろと任せてくれて……\nええ、とても嬉しかったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And he believed in me and entrust me with various things…\nYes‚ I was really happy about that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 257.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "（本当にそう思ってくれてる……なら嬉しいけど）\n（スリクスはステージに立つと人が変わるからなぁ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（If she really thinks that… then I'm glad.）\n（When IIIX is on stage‚ it's like a transformation…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 266.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "（今の話、どこまで本当なんだろうか……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I wonder how much of what she's saying is true…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 270.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-kor027.m4a",
      "text": "これからもマネージャーさんと、ファンの人達に\n信頼されるように頑張らないといけませんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "From now on‚ I have to work hard\nto earn the trust of my manager and the fans.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 278.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-kor028.m4a",
      "text": "さて。それでは、次の曲――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then. Now‚ onto the next song――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 282.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_01_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "（……全部が全部、嘘ではなければいいんだけどな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…I just hope that none of it is a lie.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 286.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}